 Defined in config.yaml as DECAY_STRATEGIES map. Applied per-edge based on edge type (or target node type for ambiguous cases).

 Confidence-weighted edge formula (per Gemini enhancement #5):

 final_weight = (tier_confidence × raw_frequency) × decay_factor(edge_type, age_days)

 tier_confidence:
   Tier 1 (structured JSON): 1.0
   Tier 2 (regex):           0.7
   Tier 3 (LLM NER):         0.85

 Prevents Tier 3 hallucinations from drowning out Tier 1 anchors while still letting LLM-found 2nd/3rd-order edges compete fairly with regex-found ones.

